import { Nav, Bars, NavMenu, NavBtn, NavBtnLink, Logo, MenuDiv, NavLink } from "./styled"

import React from 'react';

const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <Nav>

            <Logo>dimitri.finger</Logo>

            <Bars />
            <NavMenu isOpen={isOpen}>
                <NavLink >
                    About
                </NavLink>
                <NavLink to='/services' >
                    Services
                </NavLink>
                <NavLink to='/contact-us'>
                    Contact Us
                </NavLink>
                <NavLink to='/sign-up'>
                    Sign Up
                </NavLink>
            </NavMenu>
            <NavBtn>
                <NavBtnLink to='/login'>Sign In</NavBtnLink>
            </NavBtn>
        </Nav>
    )
}

export default Navbar
